      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CYCLONE TILLY (1) scored (16.90) last time out over 300m at this track ten weeks ago. Has never missed the frame here from three starts. Rates strongly and will go close from the inside draw. CANYA CURRENCY (2) had a tricky draw last time and although midfield in fourth wasn't far away finishing 1.1 lengths from the winner (16.93). Solid record here at the distance winning two races. Should be about the money. PACIFIC HOLLY (8) resumed from a break finishing fifth (20.07) at Q Lakeside in a Grade 5. Has a good record at this journey. The form out of last race has been strong. Has ability and can atone. SHE'S A KIWI (3) is in fine form and looks a good top-three chance again.",
